data.description: ** At This Price Point, This Will Not Last** Attention Realtors! Don't miss out on this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasting 1200 square feet of living space. Enjoy ample room to spread out and relax, highlighted by a generously sized master suite with a spacious closet, a tastefully appointed dining room, and a chic living room perfect for entertaining guests. An inviting kitchen for culinary adventures, exterior lighting for added ambiance, a shaded yard offering respite from the sun, and a reliable security system for peace of mind. This property offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and security - schedule your showing today!
